name: MiniTipi Play Tent (with 4 x hardwood dowels)
description: Shipping is free. Only available in Australia. MiniTipi play tent provides a fun and stimulating environment for your child. The play tent can be a play store, a space rocket, a ship or wherever your imagination takes you! MiniTipi play tent lets children interact and have a fun time. It’s through interaction and play children develop social and cognitive skills, and are able to mature emotionally and gain the self-confidence to try new experiences and environments. Tipi Height: approx 1300mm Side width (Including poles): approx 930mm Pole Height: approx 1800mm Materials The MiniTipi is made of 100% cotton and available in white fabric with red and green print. The doors has velcro tabs for privacy. The Tipi has four sides – one printed shop front, one door side and two white sides. Bright Red Polyester rope holding poles in place. The hardwood dowels are made of PEFC-certified wood sources. Care Advice Cold handwash Cool iron inside out Dry flat Do not soak Do not bleach Do not dry clean

name: Animal Friends Memory Game
description: Shipping is free in Australia, UK, Ireland and Scandinavia. Welcome our newest product, the Animal Friends Memory Game. It introduces our eight new friends. name: Super Places Canberra Poster
description: Shipping is free in Australia, UK, Ireland and Scandinavia. Canberra is the Capital of Australia and an iconic city designed by Walter Burley Griffin. It truly was a pleasure to interpret and illustrate the city with so many architectural treasures. The Canberra Super Places Collection is carefully illustrated with a timeless classic feel. Hot air balloons, ferris wheel and tulips reminds of the festive spirit of the annual Floriade combined with more formal architectural elements such as the Australian Parliament overlooking Lake Burley Griffin. Product Information Printed on 170gsm coated paper Poster size 297mm x 420mm Printed in Canberra red, Lake blue and Black Mountain black. Delivered unframed. Rolled up in a protective mailer tube. Ships within 3 working days.

name: Super Places Strandhill Poster
description: Shipping is free in Australia, UK, Ireland and Scandinavia. Strandhill is located in the West Coast of Ireland, facing the open Atlantic and backed by the Mountain Knocknarea. The mountain is said to host Queen Maeves’s Tomb, and Knocknarea seems to have been a major place of ritual and meeting in the Neolithic era. Today Strandhill is a very friendly place, a small place with a big heart. It also hosts some of the most amazing surf brakes in the West Coast of Ireland, only crowded by seals and the occasional dolphin. The Strandhill illustration is inpired by stories from growing up on the mountain, playing among the ivy clad walls and hiding in the green lush Glen. A very special place. Product Information Printed on 170gsm coated paper Poster size 297mm x 420mm Delivered unframed. Rolled up in a protective mailer tube. Ships within 3 working days.
